description:
MON 10/3 - The Breakfast Club reacts to the news that Kim K was robbed at gunpoint in her Paris hotel while Kanye was performing in NY! The hee-haw goes to those finding humor in the tragic situation, sparking memories of robbery stories. Survivors, please chime in.
